quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,160,"Àyàfi àwọn tó ronú pìwàdà, tí wọ́n ṣe àtúnṣe, tí wọ́n sì ṣàfi hàn òdodo, nítorí náà, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni Mo máa gba ìronúpìwàdà wọn. Èmi sì ni Olùgba-ìronúpìwàdà, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run."
  2,161,"Dájúdájú àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́, tí wọ́n sì kú nígbà tí wọ́n jẹ́ aláìgbàgbọ́, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni ègún Allāhu, àti (ègún) àwọn mọlāika àti (ègún) ènìyàn pátápátá ń bẹ lórí wọn."
  2,162,"Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀. A ò níí ṣe ìyà náà ní fífúyẹ́ fún wọn A ò sì níí fún wọn ní ìsinmi (nínú Iná)."
  3,100,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí ẹ bá tẹ̀lé apá kan nínú àwọn tí A fún ní tírà, wọ́n máa da yín padà lẹ́yìn ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo yín sí ipò aláìgbàgbọ́."
  3,101,"Báwo ni ẹ̀yin ṣe lè ṣàì gbàgbọ́, ẹ̀yin mà ni wọ́n ń ké àwọn āyah Allāhu fún, Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀ sì wà láààrin yín! Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá dúró ṣinṣin ti Allāhu, A ti tọ́ ọ sí ọ̀nà tààrà.1 {1}",footnotes:1:[Kíyè sí i, gbólóhùn yìí, “Òjíṣẹ́ Rẹ̀ sì wà láààrin yín!” Ìyẹn ṣíwájú kí ó tó kú - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -. Àmọ́ lẹ́yìn ikú rẹ̀ - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a -, kò sí láààrin wa mọ́. Irú āyah yìí wà nínú sūrah at-Taobah; 9:94 àti 105 àti sūrah an-Nisā’;  4:64.]
  3,102,"Ẹ̀yin tí ẹ gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, ẹ bẹ̀rù Allāhu bí ó ṣe tọ́ láti bẹ̀rù Rẹ̀. Ẹ̀yin kò sì gbọdọ̀ kú àyàfi kí ẹ wà ní ipò mùsùlùmí."
  4,40,"Dájúdájú Allāhu kò níí ṣàbòsí òdíwọ̀n ọmọ iná-igún. Tí ó bá jẹ iṣẹ́ rere, Ó máa ṣàdìpèlé (ẹ̀san) rẹ̀. Ó sì máa fún (olùṣe rere) ní ẹ̀san ńlá láti ọ̀dọ̀ Rẹ̀."
  4,41,"Báwo ni ọ̀rọ̀ wọn yóò ti rí nígbà tí A bá mú ẹlẹ́rìí jáde nínú ìjọ kọ̀ọ̀kan, tí A sì mú ìwọ jáde ní ẹlẹ́rìí lórí àwọn wọ̀nyí?"
  4,42,"Ní ọjọ́ yẹn, àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́, tí wọ́n sì yapa Òjíṣẹ́ náà, wọ́n á fẹ́ kí àwọn bá ilẹ̀ dọ́gba (kí wọ́n di erùpẹ̀). Wọn kò sì lè fi ọ̀rọ̀ kan pamọ́ fún Allāhu."